Field Detail

RENDERER_CLASS_NAME

public static final String RENDERER_CLASS_NAME
The default name of the item that contains the message renderer. This is used by the message factory when creating a message renderer. See FSysMessage.createRenderer(de.systemagmbh.interfaces.config.ISysConfigItem).
